title: #92Noon! Games and Guests
description: Some football fodder to open, then Stump the Snob with Cory Cove and Saucer in studio, Birk Bit starts the second hour, followed by Lavelle and some longtime Rube call-ins midway through. Darby Hendrickson reminisces Wild hockey and more to begin final stretch, and show wraps with Twins pitcher Sergio Romo!
